data.title: Pino's on Main Pizza
data.meta_description: Carryout and delivery only. Authentic Italian pizza and dishes. Appetizers. Catering. Pasta. Sandwiches. Dinner. Call today to place an order.
data.text:
Serving Family Recipes for Over 30 Years

Family and locally owned and operated for over 30 years, Pino's on Main Pizza is the only name you need to know when it comes to authentic Italian pizza and cuisine. We use only the freshest ingredients with every dish we make. Please view our menu and place your order today. We are only offering carryout and delivery service at this time. Call (815) 963-6400 to place your order.

Pizza

Bring home pizza for the entire family when you order from Pino's on Main Pizza! We offer various sizes of pies that your family will love! Call (815) 963-6400 for fast delivery.

Learn More

Appetizers and Salads

Looking for a small bite to eat at lunch or dinner? You'll love our appetizers and salads. We have soup too for those cold winter days. Call to place your order today.

Learn More

Pasta Dishes

If you're looking for authentic Italian pasta dishes, look no further than Pino's on Main Pizza. From spaghetti and lasagna to tortellini and ravioli, we've got what you're craving.

Learn More

Sandwiches and Extras

Looking for a quick bite to eat during lunch? Call Pino's on Main Pizza and sink your teeth into one of our mouthwatering sandwiches including grilled chicken and fish options!

Learn More

Dinners

Watch your favorite shows at home while enjoying an authentic Italian dinner from Pino's on Main Pizza. We have something for everyone on our dinner menu!

Learn More

Catering

Sit back and relax and let Pino's on Main Pizza do the cooking for you! We cater to small and large groups. We serve half pans (serves 6-8) or full pans (serves 12-15).
